</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="12" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="12.[685,1172,194,879]" pageId="12">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[709,824,805,826]" pageId="12">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet is derived from 
<emphasis box="[685,744,831,852]" italics="true" pageId="12">ampla</emphasis>
(= large), a Latin adjective that refers to the large size of antennomere 8.
</paragraph>
